<h2><b><b>YOUTH</b></b></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>
<h4><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/get-connected/music-and-worship/student-choirs/">WITNESS - MIDDLE SCHOOL CHOIR (GRADES 6-8)</a></h4>
<em>6:00-7:00 PM in Room 221</em></strong><br />This fun choir is open to all Middle School students. Witness participates in many fun music projects and activities throughout the year, including an annual choir our every June, as well  as performing for 15,000 people during the annual Portland's Christmas  Celebration concerts.<a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/get-connected/music-and-worship/student-choirs/"><br /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>
<h4><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/get-connected/music-and-worship/student-choirs/">PRIORITY - HIGH SCHOOL AND COLLEGE CHOIR (GRADE 9 TO AGE 20)</a></h4>
<i>6:00-7:00 PM in the Choir Room</i></strong><br />This year, Priority begins its 22nd season of ministry at Portland  Christian Center! This dynamic choir is open to all High School and  College students (up to age 20). We'd love to have you join us! We have an incredible  year planned, including an awesome 10 day summer tour in June!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/get-connected/middle-school/intensify-the-revolution/"><br /></a></p>
<h4><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/get-connected/middle-school/intensify-the-revolution/">REVOLUTION - MIDDLE SCHOOL (GRADES 6-8)</a></h4>
<p><strong><em>7:00-8:30 PM in the Fireside Room</em></strong><br />Revolution is a safe place to meet new friends and have lots of fun  together. We shatter the &ldquo;church is boring&rdquo; stereotype and give you tons  of reasons to get connected and grow in Jesus! The best part is that we  engage you and challenge you to become the person who God has created  you to be.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/get-connected/high-school/">UNVEILED - HIGH SCHOOL (GRADES 9-12)</a></h4>
<p><em><strong>7:00-8:30 PM in the Youth Center</strong></em><br />We are a group of young people who are passionate about discovering who we are, who God is, and what this life is all about. 2 Corinthians 3:16-18 tells us that when we turn to Christ, the veil is taken away, and we are able to see clearly for the first time. That&rsquo;s when the adventure of living for God begins! So come check out what&rsquo;s going on at Unveiled!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
